<h1>jQuery Lifestream Plug-in</h1>

<p><img src="http://christianv.github.com/jquery-lifestream/design/logo_v1_64.png" alt="jQuery Lifestream Logo">
</p>

<p>Show a stream of your online activity.<br>
Check out <a href="http://christianv.github.com/jquery-lifestream/example.html" title="Example page">the example</a> or create <a href="http://christianv.github.com/jquery-lifestream/me/">your own lifestream</a> instantly.</p>

<p><a href="http://twitter.com/jq_lifestream"><img src="http://f.cl.ly/items/2z1p0w320g1q0T061m1u/twitter_follow.png" alt="Follow us on twitter">
</a></p>

<h2>Requirements</h2>

<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.jquery.com">jQuery 1.4.2+</a></li>
</ul>

